Jimmy Kimmel on Monday found a strange Donald Trump appearance hosted by a Florida fan club, where tickets included a discount for Tony Roma’s ribs. “For real,” Kimmel insisted. Indeed, the Club 45 website says that members enjoy a discount at the Tony Roma’s in the Hilton Palm Beach Airport hotel, where the group meets and where Trump spoke to them on Monday. Kimmel noted that the event included a 5-year-old girl asking a question about inflation ― and that the girl was still there, watching, when Trump went on a tangent about rape, using the word over and over again as he warned about the supposed dangers of immigrants during a xenophobic rant. See more in his Tuesday night monologue: